{
    "id": "electronics/tin-soldering-iron",
    "title": "Tin a Soldering Iron",
    "description": "Prepare your soldering iron for clean joints by tinning the tip.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/electronics_tin_soldering_iron_tip.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/orion.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Good to see you progressing! Before soldering, lay out a silicone mat, secure your work in helping hands, plug in your station, keep a brass tip cleaner nearby, and have a damp sponge ready. Ventilation and eye protection are mandatory before heat-up.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep-station",
                    "text": "Iron is heating up.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "4379a2f8-7cec-4bea-949b-ad50514d36ff",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "87f670ce-3630-42bb-84c0-9243cf630d05",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "cd0e1512-9b4e-4450-92ab-b298852ca5e7",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "3dbf1701-5cc0-4443-b9bf-4275b33513d0",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "prep-station",
            "text": "Confirm your safety setup: goggles on, extractor running, iron parked on its stand, and no loose scraps near the hot tip.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "tin",
                    "text": "Safety checks complete."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "troubleshoot-station",
                    "text": "Something is unsafe or unstable."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "tin",
            "text": "Once the tip is hot, melt a little solder across it, then wipe on the damp sponge to leave a thin, shiny layer that resists oxidation.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "verify-tip",
                    "text": "Tip looks shiny."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "troubleshoot-tip",
                    "text": "Tip looks dull, blackened, or solder won't wet."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "troubleshoot-station",
            "text": "Pause before continuing. Unplug the iron, clear clutter, re-seat the stand, and restart only after ventilation and PPE are confirmed.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep-station",
                    "text": "Station corrected; re-check safety."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "troubleshoot-tip",
            "text": "Recover the tip: wipe on brass wool, add fresh solder and a touch of flux, then re-tin. If the tip pits or flakes, stop and replace the tip before retrying.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "tin",
                    "text": "I recovered or replaced the tip; re-test tinning."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "verify-tip",
            "text": "Verification checkpoint: the tip should hold a smooth silver film and transfer heat quickly to a scrap lead without smoke spikes.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Verified: stable tinning achieved.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "4379a2f8-7cec-4bea-949b-ad50514d36ff",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "87f670ce-3630-42bb-84c0-9243cf630d05",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "cd0e1512-9b4e-4450-92ab-b298852ca5e7",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "3dbf1701-5cc0-4443-b9bf-4275b33513d0",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Nice work! A tinned tip makes future joints easier and cleaner. Unplug the iron and let it cool safely.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "All done."
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "rewards": [
        {
            "id": "fb60696a-6c94-4e5e-9277-b62377ee6d73",
            "count": 1
        }
    ],
